snippet.title: Minecraft x Lightyear DLC – Official Trailer
snippet.description: After a crash landing on an alien planet, Buzz Lightyear goes on the space adventure of a lifetime! Download the Lightyear DLC for Minecraft to take on five missions, use nifty gadgets, and drive awesome vehicles. Be sure to head on over to the Dressing Room for a free Lightyear themed Character Creator item!
